Package: appimg
Version: 0.1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, libgirepository-1.0-1, desktop-file-utils, shared-mime-info
Maintainer: AppImg Team <appimg@example.com>
Description: macOS-style AppImage installer for Linux
 AppImg provides a macOS-style drag-and-drop installation experience
 for AppImage files on Linux. It features a clean GTK4 interface,
 sound notifications, and easy management of installed applications.
